<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<link rel="icon" href="/img/logo.svg">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>İTÜ Raptiye</title>
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
		integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/default.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">

</head>

<body>
	<!-- Fixed Navbar -->
	<div id="navbar">
		<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
	</div>

	<div id="content-wrapper">
		<div id="section1" class="section">
			<h2>İkinci El Sahibinden Al</h2>
			<p>İtülülerden uygun fiyata ders kitaplarını, mutfak malzemelerini, spor aksesuarlarını karşıla.</p>
		</div>
		<div id="section2" class="section">
			<h2>Kiradan Eşya Al</h2>
			<p>Günlük lazım olan bisiklet, krampon, sözlük vs. aradığın ihtiyaçlarını kiradan al.</p>
		</div>
		<div id="section3" class="section">
			<h2>Harf Notu Hesapla</h2>
			<p>Matematik, Fizik, Kimya notunu herkesten önce öğren.</p>
		</div>
		<div id="section4" class="section">
			<h2>İlan Ver</h2>
			<p>Dilediğin her şeyi kolayca satışa çıkar, kirala ve alıcısıyla buluştur.</p>
		</div>
		<div id="section5" class="section">
			<h2>İş Bul</h2>
			<p>Günübirlik veya uzun vadeli sana uygun ne varsa başvurabilirsin.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="footer">
		<%- include('partials/footer') %>
	</div>

	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

	<!-- for scrolling between pages -->
	<script>
		let currentSection = 0;
		const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.section');
		const numSections = sections.length;

		window.addEventListener('wheel', (event) => {
			// Check scroll direction
			if (event.deltaY > 0) {
				// Scroll down
				currentSection = Math.min(currentSection + 1, numSections - 1);
			} else {
				// Scroll up
				currentSection = Math.max(currentSection - 1, 0);
			}

			sections[currentSection].scrollIntoView({
				behavior: 'smooth',
				block: 'start' // Aligns the section to the top
			});

			// Prevent default scroll
			event.preventDefault();
		});
	</script>
</body>

</html>



